            "author_association": "MEMBER",
            "body": "Without looking into the details, I'm skeptical about the include path. Why do you need it in the first place? You are compiling modules inside of the same package, a local import should just work. Mixing different sub-directories as base for imports seems unnecessarily confusing.",
